lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:15:07.000Z","msg":"可以查下「皮肉」日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685ee33f80322374e7cee7c775650794f5030236","tid":2104073,"uid":331822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c00469121ea04ccaa49894159f54d28bde60921","tid":2104073,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ec5aec6fe902372a275926e2f207885321abfdd","tid":2104073,"uid":37666,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"我都唔明大陸點解比佢起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺明落自己面啦<br />\n仲有喎佢隔一兩年就叫反日<br />\n擺明叫啲大陸憤青整爛佢啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"佢地doublethink freedom = 擁護極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"第日又玩反日，然後成個FREEDOM砌左就好笑"},{"pid":"bf9a608d3b9ce37d3f7a5fc314d3321056d6b022","tid":2104073,"uid":311547,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"ひにく 【皮肉】<br />\n這是「諷刺」的意思，怎麼「皮肉」會跟「諷刺」有關呢？其實是佛教的一個故事。大意是菩提達摩要去世時，問了一下四位第子，誰能得到真傳，四人各講了他們的想法後，菩提分別給他們下評語，一個只得到「皮」、一個只得到「肉」，後面兩個分別得到「骨」跟「髓」(得到了心中的想法)。意思是說後面的兩個比較有真傳到。前面兩個只得「皮肉」，就是只有表面。<br />\n<br />\n後來轉化為當講話表裡不一時，如講好話，可是內心卻是覺得人家不好，被人聽出來時，別人就會覺得你是在講「皮肉」，而不是講心中的真話(骨髓)。"},{"pid":"0c43766e157daa2042b6aeaa138547692bf8a954","tid":2104073,"uid":85965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"架仔comment全部都係串緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係冇自由既國家整個自由高達真係好諷刺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840fbd7bd23b7d13f1e6f2ae8ef3f2a243cbccec","tid":2104073